<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <head>
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/postDetail.css">
    </head> 
<body>
    <%- include('partials/headerLoggedOn') %> 

      <div class="card post-detail">
        <div class="card-header title">
          <%= post.name %> 
        </div>
        <div class="card-header username">
          <a class="streched-link" href="/users/userdetail"> <%= post.username %> </a>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <section>
            <img src="/<%= post.image %> " class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <p class="card-text description">With supporting text below as a natural lead-in to additional content.</p>
          </section>
          <section>
            <h5 class="card-title">Ingredients</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. In placeat dicta eaque adipisci quis. Soluta autem odio, dignissimos voluptatem eaque quidem omnis reiciendis assumenda dolorum quo rem dolore ipsam nemo. Velit facilis, officiis eum vero eligendi repudiandae ipsa dolore enim autem porro molestias error in debitis, totam corrupti veritatis soluta.</p>
            <h5 class="card-title instructions-title">Instructions</h5>
            <p class="card-text"><%= post.preparation %> </p>
          </section>
          <section>
            <h5 class="card-title">Comments</h5>
            <a class="streched-link" href="/users/userdetail"><p class="post-username-comment">nombreusuario</p></a>
            <p class="post-comment-content">Muy buenooo!!</p>
            <br>
            <a class="streched-link" href="/users/userdetail"><p class="post-username-comment">nombreusuario</p></a>
            <p class="post-comment-content">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Consectetur nulla omnis laborum dolor quae maiores nam veritatis quaerat numquam perspiciatis!</p>
            <br>
            <a class="streched-link" href="/users/userdetail"><p class="post-username-comment">nombreusuario</p></a>
            <p class="post-comment-content">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Vel, alias?</p>
            <br>
            <h5 class="card-title leave-comment-title">Leave a comment</h5>
            <form class="form-comment">
                  <div class="input-group">
                    <textarea class="form-control" aria-label="With textarea"></textarea>
                  </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Comment</button>
              </form>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %> 
</body>
</html>